WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.679
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:12.256
Well, it's Diana, my beautiful bride, and me. We're excited to be here today.

00:00:12.257 --> 00:00:17.608
I try to embarrass her as much as I can when she's sitting next to me.

00:00:17.609 --> 00:00:21.687
You don't know how many times we do these takes, and I try to be funny.

00:00:21.688 --> 00:00:33.369
I told her, "It's making her laugh."If you can't have fun doing what you're doing, then why do it, right?

00:00:33.370 --> 00:00:36.394
It's exciting times. This is what Jesus is talking to us about.

00:00:36.395 --> 00:00:41.679
Nothing is going to happen in the natural unless we pray it through in the spiritual first.

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:47.399
We must intercede and pray for what's coming. He talked about it even today.

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:52.055
I was driving around, and Diana had to go into the grocery store.

00:00:52.056 --> 00:00:59.822
The Lord started talking about cars, people driving around in their cars, and the cars looking like they were on fire when the glory was on them.

00:00:59.823 --> 00:01:09.465
He said, "Brandon, I'm going to do something very unusual."And I said, "Lord, what is that?"He said, "The fire was on buildings last time whenever Azusa Street happened.

00:01:09.466 --> 00:01:15.371
People saw fire on the buildings when Rodney Howard-Browne held meetings in Fort Worth, Texas.

00:01:15.373 --> 00:01:20.909
The building looked like it was on fire, and the fire department came, but the building was not on fire.

00:01:20.910 --> 00:01:35.993
It was on fire with the Holy Ghost, and they were seeing in the spirit realm a building that was on fire."The Lord told me, "Brandon, what I'm about to do is that when people are driving around on the streets, it's going to look like their car is on fire.

00:01:35.994 --> 00:01:43.914
I'm going to show up in their car as they're interceding, driving around the city, and your car is going to look like you're on fire.

00:01:43.915 --> 00:01:56.205
People are going to be staring, thinking your car is on fire, as a sign and a wonder in these last days—not just on buildings, but on you when you walk in like Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego.

00:01:56.206 --> 00:02:06.087
You're in a Holy Ghost fire. They were in an actual fire. But I'm talking about a real fire that they see on us.

00:02:06.088 --> 00:02:11.910
They will go, 'What is going on with that guy? He's on fire.'It's the glory.

00:02:11.911 --> 00:02:21.919
It's the glory."Ladies and gentlemen, it's time to anticipate the demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:29.234
Over the past 30 or 40 years, or whatever you've had in your life, the Lord has shown me, He said, "Brandon, it's been a cultivation with folks.

00:02:29.235 --> 00:02:38.695
Not everybody is going to walk in the greater supernatural miracles because they're not there yet. They'll try to take the glory for it. Do you understand?

00:02:38.696 --> 00:02:56.158
God will use you in an unusual way if you know how to deflect the glory to Him."The Lord told me, "If you don't take the glory, Brandon, I'll use you to do great and mighty things.

00:02:56.159 --> 00:03:03.383
As long as you always deflect it like a mirror, deflecting the glory to Him. You attract to deflect.

00:03:03.384 --> 00:03:14.493
As long as you deflect the glory in these last days, I'll use you mightily.""But there are many people who will not deflect it. They'll try to take it.

00:03:14.494 --> 00:03:24.609
And He said, 'I will not share my glory with any man.'For what I'm about to do in these last days, no one has ever seen what's about to happen.

00:03:24.610 --> 00:03:32.599
No eye has seen, no ear has heard, nor has it entered into the heart of man the things that God has prepared for those that love Him.

00:03:32.600 --> 00:03:43.439
Listen, ladies and gentlemen, God is about to show up and show off in your life in an unprecedented way that's going to be shock and awe.

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:47.323
But He will not share His glory with what's about to take place.

00:03:47.324 --> 00:04:00.329
And if He can trust you to deflect it as a general, then He'll use you mightily."He showed me it's going to be like a change in command in the natural, like we have in the army.

00:04:00.330 --> 00:04:05.090
We have the generals, then it goes to lieutenant generals, and it keeps going down, right?

00:04:05.091 --> 00:04:10.188
The Lord showed me that it is just like that in the spirit realm.

00:04:10.189 --> 00:04:17.708
And the ones that pay the price and are willing to say, "I deflect. Father, it's not me.

00:04:17.709 --> 00:04:23.902
It's You."I just want everybody to know immediately when you're in a crowd and you're on fire with the glory, it's all about Jesus.

00:04:23.903 --> 00:04:28.383
This isn't about attracting attention to me. This isn't about how great I am.

00:04:28.384 --> 00:04:32.034
It's about how great He is. He's able to operate through this vessel.

00:04:32.035 --> 00:04:38.564
Ladies and gentlemen, I have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power may be of Him and not of me. This is important.

00:04:38.565 --> 00:05:01.798
With what we're about to see—when we see the legs, the arms, the ears, and the dead being raised—we must remember we have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of me.

00:05:01.799 --> 00:05:12.143
I decrease, He increases. As long as we have a heart where He is increasing and we are decreasing, we are deflecting and looking at Him.

00:05:12.144 --> 00:05:17.714
He is the potter, I am the clay. He is not sharing His glory with anyone.

00:05:17.715 --> 00:05:25.730
He could use anybody, but He's not sharing the glory. It's all about Him and nothing about me.

00:05:25.731 --> 00:05:33.451
I'm just a vessel that He uses in these end times. Do you understand? We attract to deflect, and it's very important.

00:05:33.452 --> 00:05:50.478
The Lord showed me today that as we are getting ready to see demonstrations and manifestations like we've never seen before, He said, "If you want to be a general in my army, know that I will not share my glory with anybody."People will say, "Well, look at him.

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:57.279
He's on fire. Can you believe that? Did you know that Sister Diana has raised 30 people from the dead?

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:02.954
Boy, she's something, isn't she?"She's a child of the King, and I'm a child of the King.

00:06:02.955 --> 00:06:08.959
We're all just doing exactly what He's called us to do, and He can use anybody.

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:17.918
Keep your eyes on Him and stay focused. It's important that you do this. You need to hear me because of what He's told me is coming.

00:06:17.919 --> 00:06:25.853
Unusual signs and wonders beyond anybody's comprehension are about to take place in the body of Christ.

00:06:25.854 --> 00:06:34.673
Unusual demonstrations, unusual miracles, things we've never seen before.

00:06:34.674 --> 00:06:43.523
If God showed up with the glory on Moses's face, He said, "Brandon, I'm going to show up with even greater glory on you.

00:06:43.524 --> 00:06:49.999
Watch if you learn to deflect."Keep learning. Keep dying to self.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:54.749
That's why the Apostle Paul said, "I die daily."I will not take the glory.

00:06:54.750 --> 00:07:01.748
When the shadow of Peter walked down through wherever the people were sick, the glory touched them.

00:07:01.749 --> 00:07:06.844
He didn't even have to lay hands on them; the glory of the Lord touched these people, right?

00:07:06.845 --> 00:07:13.909
The shadow touched them. When the shadow touched them, it was the glory. It wasn't him; it was just a shadow.

00:07:13.910 --> 00:07:25.276
The glory was radiating out of him so strongly and so powerfully that even the shadow touched them.

00:07:25.277 --> 00:07:33.235
That's what the Lord showed me during my prayer time all day today, just driving around. He said, "Brandon, you must keep this in mind all the time.

00:07:33.236 --> 00:07:47.621
You have a treasure in an earthen vessel, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of you."This treasure that you carry—He said, "You don't share your treasure until I tell you to share it.

00:07:47.622 --> 00:07:58.770
It's not your gift. It's my gift being distributed through you. The gold and the silver are mine. The cattle are mine.

00:07:58.771 --> 00:08:10.532
The anointing and the glory are mine."This endless treasure that you carry in earthen vessels is a treasure.

00:08:10.533 --> 00:08:15.427
The power of the Holy Spirit is a treasure in an earthen vessel.

00:08:15.428 --> 00:08:21.138
And He showed me a vast supply. And He said, "The supply will never run dry, Brandon.

00:08:21.139 --> 00:08:25.642
It will never run dry with anything that I've called you to do.

00:08:25.643 --> 00:08:37.038
There is a vast supply."Come to the river. Hallelujah. I feel the Holy Spirit right now.

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:51.437
He showed me this treasure and all these coins, and He said, "Just because you have it and you operate in it, Brandon, doesn't mean it's for you to just do what you want to do with it."You are a steward of what I've called you to do.

00:08:51.438 --> 00:08:56.639
Listen, you are a steward of the money, of the wealth, of the glory.

00:08:56.640 --> 00:09:01.919
That's what I want to say. The vast supply, the treasure in earthen vessels.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:08.238
You have that treasure inside of you, ladies and gentlemen, and you're a steward of it.

00:09:08.239 --> 00:09:19.599
'What do you want me to do with this, Lord?'And He said, 'You don't let everybody touch the treasure, and you don't tell everybody about it.'Because it's precious.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:32.799
The way you guard it and you protect it. And as you distribute it, you distribute the coins out—the treasure in earthen vessels—you distribute those out to the people that He tells you to.

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:43.853
This is exactly what I've asked you to do today. Jesus said, 'I do nothing unless my Father instructs me to do it.'Even if He thought, 'Well, I'm the Son of God.

00:09:43.854 --> 00:09:47.536
Are you kidding me? I can do whatever I want to do. Are you kidding me?

00:09:47.537 --> 00:09:53.049
I'm Jesus.'No, He went about it even more humbled and dead to self.

00:09:53.050 --> 00:10:01.832
'I do nothing unless I hear my Father tell me to do it,'regardless of what He thought or what He could have done.

00:10:01.833 --> 00:10:13.652
'I only do what I'm instructed to by my Father.'And that's exactly how He operated the whole time He was walking underneath the glory, and that's what we should do.

00:10:13.653 --> 00:10:17.607
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, and it's coins. It's beautiful gold.

00:10:17.608 --> 00:10:25.195
It's beautiful diamonds. What do you do with that in distributing it out to the people? Only do what the Father tells you to do.

00:10:25.196 --> 00:10:33.169
I have a treasure, and in these scriptures that He gives me today, the excellency of the power will be known to Him.

00:10:33.170 --> 00:10:39.611
I attract to deflect, and I always make sure I'm never going to share the glory with the Lord.

00:10:39.612 --> 00:10:43.175
It's all about Him and nothing about me. Does that make sense?

00:10:43.176 --> 00:10:50.398
You have to keep this in your heart. He said, 'Those that do this, I will use even greater.

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:54.559
They'll be ranked in the military in the spiritual realm.'Who will be used?

00:10:54.560 --> 00:11:14.479
He said, 'There's a lot of them I will not be able to trust because the moment of fame, the moment of clout, when they start getting huge on YouTube, huge on the news, or Daystar calls you up, or whoever—"Hey, my goodness, we heard you raised five people from the dead!"Well, of course, don't you know how much time I've spent fasting and praying?

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:24.688
Don't you know how much I've done?'It's all about Jesus. I just need you to know this. This is what He's instructing me today.

00:11:24.689 --> 00:11:37.537
And it was very beautiful, but it was talking about how it was going to be in the days ahead, just right here in front of us.

00:11:37.538 --> 00:11:45.599
Glory to God. Hallelujah! I'm so thankful for a praying wife, that we seek Him together.

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:58.792
I'm telling you, it is so important to pray and to seek Him together with your spouse, and that's why you don't hook yourself up with a dead horse.

00:11:58.793 --> 00:12:02.171
'Well, I'm going to pray and get that person saved. I'm going to do this.

00:12:02.172 --> 00:12:09.439
I'm going to do that.'No. Do not marry and be unequally yoked with unbelievers.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:15.518
Find a believing believer if you're going to get married, or don't get married at all.

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:22.270
You need to find a believing believer to get married to. I'm telling you, there's a lot of seeker-friendly...

00:12:22.271 --> 00:12:28.340
You're going to see people that think, 'Well, we have to change things on the stage.

00:12:28.341 --> 00:12:33.506
We have to change things because we're losing numbers. We have to keep relevant.

00:12:33.507 --> 00:12:37.449
We have to do these things.'And, 'We have to change our stage.

00:12:37.450 --> 00:12:51.966
We have to change our packaging because we're losing the people.'And the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, if you're standing in the middle of a field in a cow patty pasture, and you see poop all over the place, but people are gathered up...

00:12:51.967 --> 00:13:08.955
If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto me.'If the glory is there, I don't care if you're standing in waist-high mud, you're going to attract people like moths to a light, like these stupid flies flying around here trying to get around this light right now that I keep trying to kill.

00:13:08.956 --> 00:13:19.050
I'm telling you, if He be lifted up, regardless of what it is, what people are attracted to is not how pretty your stage is or how great your music is.

00:13:19.051 --> 00:13:31.416
It's the glory. It's the glory! I've seen it. Even when Reinhard Bonnke did his meetings and crusades in Africa, four or five million people showed up, right?

00:13:31.417 --> 00:13:36.600
But he had just a little tractor-trailer and this little stage with this backdrop, nothing really cool.

00:13:36.601 --> 00:13:45.457
But the presence of the Lord was there, and you don't have to dress up anything when the presence of the Lord is there.

00:13:45.457 --> 00:13:51.359
They're just coming to see somebody burn, to be on fire for Jesus.

00:13:51.360 --> 00:13:58.972
But a lot of people who are dead spiritually try to dress it up really pretty and put a bow on it and think it's the glory, and it's not.

00:13:58.973 --> 00:14:12.159
And you're going to see what was once alive in the body of Christ—before that was an oasis in the desert—become a cesspool because they've cut themselves off from the vine.

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:19.505
They are no longer attached. And it's happening more and more and more, from what I hear. And you go, 'What happened?

00:14:19.506 --> 00:14:28.192
They were a place of refreshing.'They detached themselves, and now they try to decorate it and make it look pretty because it's work to get on the vine.

00:14:28.193 --> 00:14:35.439
It's work to die to self, and they don't want to do that. They go, 'Well, I don't want to do that.'Well, your flesh doesn't want to.

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:40.719
'Well, it's all right to sleep around. It's all right to drink.

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:43.453
It's all right to party. It's all right to do all these things.

00:14:43.454 --> 00:14:50.552
We're not going to judge you.'Are you serious? We're going to walk in grace and mercy.

00:14:50.553 --> 00:14:58.854
I'm going to tell you this: you are either hot for Jesus or cold. If you're lukewarm, He'll spew you out of His mouth.

00:14:58.855 --> 00:15:06.326
And people who think they can live a compromising lifestyle and make it in the rapture, you have another thing coming.

00:15:06.327 --> 00:15:14.799
So many of you are going to be taken aback by what's about to take place. A great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:21.679
You're not going to live like the world and be a purified bride that's going to come and go in the rapture.

00:15:21.680 --> 00:15:28.621
There were five that had their lamps full and five that didn't. Which one are you? So, that's what I had for you.

00:15:28.622 --> 00:15:41.518
I just want you to get on fire for Jesus and know what's about to take place as we see all these major signs, as we see all this stuff going on.

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:47.394
I'm just in awe that we're right there. We're seeing the covenant with many.

00:15:47.394 --> 00:15:51.821
We're seeing it talked about. We're seeing all these things, the red heifer and all this stuff.

00:15:51.822 --> 00:15:58.512
And I'm like, 'Wow, folks, this is so cool.'I'm excited about the prayer conference in the fall.

00:15:58.513 --> 00:16:04.100
Sister Billye always holds her prayer conference in the fall in October in Branson.

00:16:04.101 --> 00:16:07.702
And the Lord keeps showing me Branson for the major revival.

00:16:07.703 --> 00:16:12.912
I kept seeing visions of Branson today, and the leaves are still on the trees.

00:16:12.913 --> 00:16:21.517
It was beautiful outside, and there was an anticipation for something amazing about to take place in Branson, Missouri.

