And he said, 'Watch the scales be leveled, and they're going to flip today.'There's a time frame in the spirit realm that we've been waiting on as a body.

00:21:02.146 --> 00:21:20.639
You say, 'Why hasn't it happened yet? Why hasn't it manifested yet?'The time frame and the scale are about to flip like a paradigm shift.

